CalculatedFields.Name: Avg Wait Time Today - Voice
CalculatedFields.Expression: if (data.totalWaitCountVoiceToday > 0) return Math.round(data.totalWaitTimeVoiceToday / data.totalWaitCountVoiceToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: Avg Wait Time Today
CalculatedFields.Expression: var totalWaitCountToday = data.totalWaitCountVoiceToday + data.totalWaitCountCallbackToday + data.totalWaitCountChatToday + data.totalWaitCountEmailToday + data.totalWaitCountMessageToday; if (totalWaitCountToday > 0) return Math.round((data.totalWaitTimeVoiceToday + data.totalWaitTimeCallbackToday + data.totalWaitTimeChatToday + data.totalWaitTimeEmailToday + data.totalWaitTimeMessageToday) / totalWaitCountToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Abandoned
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAbandoned / data.numOffered)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Abandoned Today - Voice
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAbandonedToday / data.numOfferedToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Service Level
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnswered - data.numOverSla) / (data.numAnswered + data.numAbandoned + (data.includeFlowoutsInSlaCalculation ? data.numFlowedOut : 0) - (data.includeShortAbandonedInSla ? data.numShortAbandoned : 0))

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Service Level Today - Voice
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredToday - data.numOverSlaToday) / (data.numAnsweredToday + data.numAbandonedToday + (data.includeFlowoutsInSlaCalculation ? data.numFlowedOutToday : 0) - (data.includeShortAbandonedInSla ? data.numShortAbandonedToday : 0))

CalculatedFields.Name: Customers Waiting
CalculatedFields.Expression: return data.customersWaitingVoice + data.customersWaitingEmail + data.customersWaitingChat + data.customersWaitingCallback + data.customersWaitingMessage

CalculatedFields.Name: Offered Today
CalculatedFields.Expression: return data.numOfferedToday + data.numOfferedTodayCallback + data.numOfferedTodayChat + data.numOfferedTodayEmail + data.numOfferedTodayMessage

CalculatedFields.Name: Answered Today
CalculatedFields.Expression: return data.numAnsweredToday + data.numAnsweredTodayCallback + data.numAnsweredTodayChat + data.numAnsweredTodayEmail + data.numAnsweredTodayMessage

CalculatedFields.Name: Abandoned Today
CalculatedFields.Expression: return data.numAbandonedToday + data.numAbandonedTodayCallback + data.numAbandonedTodayChat + data.numAbandonedTodayEmail + data.numAbandonedTodayMessage

CalculatedFields.Name: Flowed Out Today
CalculatedFields.Expression: return data.numFlowedOutToday + data.numFlowedOutTodayCallback + data.numFlowedOutTodayChat + data.numFlowedOutTodayEmail + data.numFlowedOutTodayMessage

CalculatedFields.Name: Customers Interacting
CalculatedFields.Expression: return data.customersInteractingVoice + data.customersInteractingChat + data.customersInteractingEmail + data.customersInteractingCallback + data.customersInteractingMessage

CalculatedFields.Name: Avg Wait Time Today - Callback
CalculatedFields.Expression: if (data.totalWaitCountCallbackToday > 0) return Math.round(data.totalWaitTimeCallbackToday / data.totalWaitCountCallbackToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: Avg Wait Time Today - Chat
CalculatedFields.Expression: if (data.totalWaitCountChatToday > 0) return Math.round(data.totalWaitTimeChatToday / data.totalWaitCountChatToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: Avg Wait Time Today - Email
CalculatedFields.Expression: if (data.totalWaitCountEmailToday > 0) return Math.round(data.totalWaitTimeEmailToday / data.totalWaitCountEmailToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: Avg Wait Time
CalculatedFields.Expression: var totalWaitCount = data.totalWaitCount + data.totalWaitCountCallback + data.totalWaitCountChat + data.totalWaitCountEmail; if (totalWaitCount > 0) return Math.round((data.totalWaitTime + data.totalWaitTimeCallback + data.totalWaitTimeChat + data.totalWaitTimeEmail) / totalWaitCount)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Abandoned Today - Chat
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAbandonedTodayChat / data.numOfferedTodayChat)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Abandoned Today - Email
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAbandonedTodayEmail / data.numOfferedTodayEmail)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Abandoned Today - Callback
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAbandonedTodayCallback / data.numOfferedTodayCallback)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Service Level Today - Chat
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredTodayChat - data.numOverSlaTodayChat) / (data.numAnsweredTodayChat + data.numAbandonedTodayChat + (data.includeFlowoutsInSlaCalculation ? data.numFlowedOutTodayChat : 0) - (data.includeShortAbandonedInSla ? data.numShortAbandonedTodayChat : 0))

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Service Level Today - Email
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredTodayEmail - data.numOverSlaTodayEmail) / (data.numAnsweredTodayEmail + data.numAbandonedTodayEmail + (data.includeFlowoutsInSlaCalculation ? data.numFlowedOutTodayEmail : 0) - (data.includeShortAbandonedInSla ? data.numShortAbandonedTodayEmail : 0))

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Service Level Today - Callback
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredTodayCallback - data.numOverSlaTodayCallback) / (data.numAnsweredTodayCallback + data.numAbandonedTodayCallback + (data.includeFlowoutsInSlaCalculation ? data.numFlowedOutTodayCallback : 0) - (data.includeShortAbandonedInSla ? data.numShortAbandonedTodayCallback : 0))

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Service Level Today - All
CalculatedFields.Expression: var answered = (data.numAnsweredToday||0)+(data.numAnsweredTodayChat||0)+(data.numAnsweredTodayEmail||0)+(data.numAnsweredTodayMessage||0)+(data.numAnsweredTodayCallback||0), overSla = (data.numOverSlaToday||0)+(data.numOverSlaTodayChat||0)+(data.numOverSlaTodayEmail||0)+(data.numOverSlaTodayMessage||0)+(data.numOverSlaTodayCallback||0), abandoned = (data.numAbandonedToday||0)+(data.numAbandonedTodayChat||0)+(data.numAbandonedTodayEmail||0)+(data.numAbandonedTodayMessage||0)+(data.numAbandonedTodayCallback||0), flowedOut = (data.numFlowedOutToday||0)+(data.numFlowedOutTodayChat||0)+(data.numFlowedOutTodayEmail||0)+(data.numFlowedOutTodayMessage||0)+(data.numFlowedOutTodayCallback||0), shortAbandoned = (data.numShortAbandonedToday||0)+(data.numShortAbandonedTodayChat||0)+(data.numShortAbandonedTodayEmail||0)+(data.numShortAbandonedTodayMessage||0)+(data.numShortAbandonedTodayCallback||0); return 100 * (answered - overSla) / (answered + abandoned + (data.includeFlowoutsInSlaCalculation ? flowedOut : 0) - (data.includeShortAbandonedInSla ? shortAbandoned : 0))

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Abandoned Today - All
CalculatedFields.Expression: var abandoned = (data.numAbandonedToday||0)+(data.numAbandonedTodayChat||0)+(data.numAbandonedTodayEmail||0)+(data.numAbandonedTodayMessage||0)+(data.numAbandonedTodayCallback||0), offered = (data.numOfferedToday||0)+(data.numOfferedTodayChat||0)+(data.numOfferedTodayEmail||0)+(data.numOfferedTodayMessage||0)+(data.numOfferedTodayCallback||0); return 100 * abandoned / offered

CalculatedFields.Name: Transferred Today - All
CalculatedFields.Expression: return (data.numTransferredToday||0) + (data.numTransferredTodayChat||0) + (data.numTransferredTodayEmail||0) + (data.numTransferredTodayMessage||0) + (data.numTransferredTodayCallback||0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Abandoned Today - Message
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAbandonedTodayMessage / data.numOfferedTodayMessage)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Service Level Today - Message
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredTodayMessage - data.numOverSlaTodayMessage) / (data.numAnsweredTodayMessage + data.numAbandonedTodayMessage + (data.includeFlowoutsInSlaCalculation ? data.numFlowedOutTodayMessage : 0) - (data.includeShortAbandonedInSla ? data.numShortAbandonedTodayMessage : 0))

CalculatedFields.Name: Avg Wait Time Today - Message
CalculatedFields.Expression: if (data.totalWaitCountMessageToday > 0) return Math.round(data.totalWaitTimeMessageToday / data.totalWaitCountMessageToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Answered Today - All
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * ((data.numAnsweredToday + data.numAnsweredTodayCallback + data.numAnsweredTodayChat + data.numAnsweredTodayEmail + data.numAnsweredTodayMessage) / (data.numOfferedToday + data.numOfferedTodayChat + data.numOfferedTodayEmail + data.numOfferedTodayCallback + data.numOfferedTodayMessage))

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Answered Today - Voice
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredToday / data.numOfferedToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Answered Today - Chat
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredTodayChat / data.numOfferedTodayChat)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Answered Today - Email
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredTodayEmail / data.numOfferedTodayEmail)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Answered Today - Callback
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredTodayCallback / data.numOfferedTodayCallback)

CalculatedFields.Name: %PCT - Answered Today - Message
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredTodayMessage / data.numOfferedTodayMessage)

CalculatedFields.Name: Agents On-Queue
CalculatedFields.Expression: return data.agentsOnQueue

CalculatedFields.Name: Agents Logged In
CalculatedFields.Expression: return data.agentsOnQueue + data.agentsOffQueue

If connecting remotely (i.e. the agent is not installed on the MiCC server itself), SQL Server Authentication may be required.

Dimensions.Name: Queue Name
Dimensions.Proxies: [{"label":"Queue Name"},{"label":"Queue Group Membership","dataSourceType":5001,"selectionsQuery":"select [Name] from CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_QueueGroup order by [Name]","valuesQuery":"select distinct q.[Name] from CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_QueueGroup qg inner join CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_QueueGroupMembers qgm on qgm.FKQueueGroup = qg.Pkey inner join CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_Queue q on q.Pkey = qgm.FKQueue where qg.[Name] in ({{filterValues}})"}]

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Handled
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim2.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{2:AgentAnswer}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Abandoned
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim2.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{2:Abandon}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Transferred
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN Dimension15 IS NULL OR dim15.ValueEncrypted = '{{15:}}' OR dim15.ValueEncrypted = '{{15:n/a}}' OR dim15.ValueEncrypted = '{{15:None}}' THEN 0 ELSE Fact0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Interflowed
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim2.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{2:Interflow}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Queued Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact1) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Talk Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact2) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE dim2.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{2:AgentAnswer}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Hold Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact3) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN Fact3 IS NOT NULL THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Wrap Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact4) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN Fact4 IS NOT NULL THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Abandoned
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * SUM(CASE WHEN dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Abandon}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Normal}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Abandon}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Normal}}') OR (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:AgentAnswer}}') OR (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Interflow}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Transferred
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * SUM(CASE WHEN Dimension15 IS NULL OR dim15.ValueEncrypted = '{{15:}}' OR dim15.ValueEncrypted = '{{15:n/a}}' OR dim15.ValueEncrypted = '{{15:None}}' THEN 0 ELSE Fact0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * SUM(CASE WHEN dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:AgentAnswer}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Abandon}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Normal}}') OR (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:AgentAnswer}}') OR (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Interflow}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Abandoned Max
CalculatedFields.Expression: MAX(CASE WHEN dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Abandon}}' THEN Fact5 ELSE 0 END)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Abandoned Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Abandon}}' THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Abandon}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Interflowed Max
CalculatedFields.Expression: MAX(CASE WHEN dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Interflow}}' THEN Fact5 ELSE 0 END)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Interflowed Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Interflow}}' THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Interflow}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Service Level
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * SUM(CASE WHEN dim10.ValueEncrypted = '{{10:Within SL}}' AND ((dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Abandon}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Normal}}') OR (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:AgentAnswer}}') OR (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Interflow}}')) THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Abandon}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Normal}}') OR (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:AgentAnswer}}') OR (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Interflow}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Handle Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact9) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN Fact9 IS NOT NULL THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Offered
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN (dim2.ValueEncrypted = '{{2:Abandon}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Normal}}') OR dim2.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{2:AgentAnswer}}', '{{2:Interflow}}', '{{2:Callback}}', '{{2:NoAnswer}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Abandoned (Short)
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim8.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{8:Short}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Abandoned (Normal)
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim8.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{8:Normal}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Ring Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact11) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Wait Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact13) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Avg number of logged-in agents
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact16) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN Fact16 IS NOT NULL THEN 900 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedDimensions.Name: Call Date_Grp - 15 min
CalculatedDimensions.Expression: concat(right(concat('0', datepart(hour, Dimension0)), 2), ':', right(concat('0', datepart(minute, Dimension0)), 2))

CalculatedDimensions.Name: Call Date_Grp - Week
CalculatedDimensions.Expression: convert(nvarchar, dateadd(dd, 1 - datepart(dw, Dimension0), Dimension0), 102) + ' - ' + convert(nvarchar, dateadd(dd, 7 - datepart(dw, Dimension0), Dimension0), 102)

DimensionTooltips.Name: Date/Time
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Full date and time of a call. During use in a summary report, this field is grouped to the nearest interval with a format of m/d/yyyy hh:mm. If added as a row or column to a summary report, the activity will be grouped by day and hour.
DimensionTooltips.UseTip: This field is your primary filter field for date range. Use this field as a filter to select a date range for your report even if you won't be including this field on the report. In addition, use this field on your report if you want your data grouped by calendar date and interval.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Queue Name
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The name of the queue.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Exit Reason
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The reason the call left the group. Possible values are Abandoned, AgentAnswered, AgentDecline, QueueUnavailable.
DimensionTooltips.UseTip:
Abandoned:  The caller disconnected while waiting in the queue. 
AgentAnswered:  The call was answered by an agent. 
AgentDecline: The call was presented to an agent and the agent declined to answer. The call may re-queue or ring another agent. 
Interflow: The call was interflowed to another queue or destination.
Transfer: The call was transferred away from the queue by the routing service.
QueueUnavailable: The queue was unavailable to accept calls.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Party Name
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The next party after the queue. Typically this will be the agent answering the call, if it was answered, or 'None' if the call was abandoned.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Answer Spectrum
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Provides a breakout of calls answered at defined spectrum thresholds measured in seconds.
DimensionTooltips.UseTip:
Example: Spectrum 1 represents call answered within 0-5 seconds, Spectrum 2 within 6-10 seconds, etc.  Defaults are 5, 10, 15, 20, 30, 40, 60, 80, 120, and
>120 seconds.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Abandon Spectrum
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Provides a breakout of calls abandoned at defined spectrum thresholds.
DimensionTooltips.UseTip:
Example: Spectrum 1 represents call abandoned within 0-5 seconds, Spectrum 2 within 6-10 seconds, etc.  Defaults are 5, 10, 15, 20, 30, 40, 60, 80, 120, and
>120 seconds.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Interflow Spectrum
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Provides a breakout of calls interflowed at defined spectrum thresholds.
DimensionTooltips.UseTip:
Example: Spectrum 1 represents calls interflowed within 0-5 seconds, Spectrum 2 within 6-10 seconds, etc.  Defaults are 5, 10, 15, 20, 30, 40, 60, 80, 120, and
>120 seconds.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Handle Spectrum
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Provides a breakout of call handle time at defined spectrum thresholds.
DimensionTooltips.UseTip:
Example: Spectrum 1 represents calls with handle time of less 10 seconds, Spectrum 2 of less than 60 seconds, etc.  Based on a default time scale (<10, <60, <180, <240, <300, <360, <420, <480,
<540, and >541 seconds).

DimensionTooltips.Name: Short Abandoned
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Specifies if the call abandoned within the Call Abandoned Parameter configured in Mitel.
DimensionTooltips.UseTip:
Abandon time is less than the Call Abandoned Parameter = Short
Abandon time is more than the Call Abandoned Parameter = Normal

DimensionTooltips.Name: Short Handle
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Specifies if the call handle time was within the Short Talk Time value configured in Mitel.
DimensionTooltips.UseTip:
Handle time is less than the Short Talk Time = Short
Handle time is more than the Short Talk Time = Normal

DimensionTooltips.Name: Service Level
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Whether or not the total queue time was within the service level defined for the queue

DimensionTooltips.Name: Account Code
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: If account codes are enabled, this will show the account code.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Media Type
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The media type of the interaction. Could be Voice, Chat, Email, Message, etc.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Conversation Type
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The type of call. For example - ACD (external call to the queue), ACDInternal (internal call to the queue).

DimensionTooltips.Name: Direction
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The direction of the call -- (Inbound or Outbound)

DimensionTooltips.Name: Transfer Destination
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The Transfer Destination of the call, if transfered.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Transfer Destination Type
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The Transfer Destination Type of the call, if transfered.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Answered Group
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The answering Agent Group.

DimensionTooltips.Name: DNIS
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The inbound number (or other address, for example email) on which the call or other interaction came in.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Area Code
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The area code of the caller, on which CallerID is available.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Country Code
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The country code of the caller, on which CallerID is available.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Queued
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: If the conversation was queued or not.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Classification Code
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: If classification codes are enabled, this will show the classification code.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Entry Reason

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Call Date_Grp - 15 min
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by 15-minute time interval.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Call Date_Grp - Half Hour
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by 30-minute time interval.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Call Date_Grp - Hour
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This field represents the hours of the day.
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: You can use this field in two ways. If you want to limit your report to certain hours of the day (8am-5pm for example) you can filter on this field. In addition, you can add this field to your report to show calls grouped by hour of the day. If you want calls grouped by date and hour of the day, consider filtering on this field, but including the Call Date/Time field instead of this one in your report.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Call Date_Grp - Weekday
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This is the day of the week (Sunday - Saturday)
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If you include this field and your time range spans multiple weeks, the calls for the day of the week will be added together. i.e. calls for Wednesday in week 1 and calls for Wednesday in week 2 will be added together for a total number of calls on Wednesdays.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Call Date_Grp - Day of Month
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This is the number day of the month (01-31).
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If your time range spans multiple months, the calls for the number days of the month will be added together. i.e. calls for June 15 and July 15 will be added together for a total number of calls under the 15 day of the month

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Call Date_Grp - Full Date
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This field represents the date and day of week and is formated as yyyy-mm-dd weekday.
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If you want to group calls by day, use this field. You cannot filter on this field as it is a calculated field. Filter on the Call Date/Time field to get the date range you want, and include this field to group the report by dates.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Call Date_Grp - Month
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by month of the year

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Call Date_Grp - Year
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by year

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Call Date_Grp - Week
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by week

FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total amount of talk time agents spent on calls in this queue.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Hold Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total amount of time callers spent on hold with agents in this queue. Note that this is time the caller was put on hold, not time they spent holding in queue before being answered.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Wrap Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total time spent in After Call Work.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Queued Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent in queue during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Talk Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent in talk during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Hold Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent in hold during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Wrap Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent in after call work during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Handle Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total time agents spend handling calls from this queue, including talk time, hold time, and after call work time.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Handle Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent being handled during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Ring Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total amount of time spent ringing.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Ring Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent ringing during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Wait Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total amount of time spent in queue or ringing.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Wait Max

FactTooltips.Name: Count - Requeues

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Login Total

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Count - Abandoned
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The number of calls abandoned.  Calls are abandoned if the caller hangs up while waiting in queue or ringing at an agent's extension.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Count - Transferred
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The number of calls that transferred to another agent.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Count - Interflowed

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Time - Queued Avg
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The average length of time calls spend in the queue, if they are queued.  This is the total queue time divided by number of calls that were queued.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Time - Talk Avg
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The average length of time an agents spend talking on calls.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Time - Hold Avg
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The average length of time agents put calls on hold.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Time - Wrap Avg

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: %Pct - Abandoned

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: %Pct - Transferred
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The percentage of calls that were transferred.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: %Pct - Answered

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Time - Abandoned Max

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Time - Abandoned Avg
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The average length of time until a call abandoned.  This is the total time until the call abandoned divided by number of calls that were abandoned.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Time - Interflowed Max
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The max length of time until a call interflowed.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Time - Interflowed Avg
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The average length of time until a call interflowed.  This is the total time until the call interflowed divided by number of calls that were interflowed.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: %Pct - Service Level
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The percentage of the service level.

CalculatedFieldTooltips.Name: Time - Handle Avg
CalculatedFieldTooltips.Tooltip: The average length of time agents are in talk, hold, or work timer for a call.

Dimensions.Name: Agent Name
Dimensions.Proxies: [{"label":"Agent Name"},{"label":"Queue Membership","dataSourceType":5002,"selectionsQuery":"select [Name] from CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_Queue order by [Name]","valuesQuery":"select distinct a.[FirstName] + ' ' + a.LastName as fullName from CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_Queue q inner join CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_QueueAgentGroupMembers qagm on qagm.FKQueue = q.Pkey inner join CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_AgentGroupMembers agm on agm.FKAgentGroup = qagm.FKAgentGroup inner join CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_Agent a on a.Pkey = agm.FKAgent where q.[Name] in ({{filterValues}})"},{"label":"Agent Group Membership","dataSourceType":5002,"selectionsQuery":"select [Name] from CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_AgentGroup order by [Name]","valuesQuery":"select distinct a.[FirstName] + ' ' + a.LastName as fullName from CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_AgentGroup ag inner join CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_AgentGroupMembers agm on agm.FKAgentGroup = ag.Pkey inner join CCMData.dbo.tblConfig_Agent a on a.Pkey = agm.FKAgent where ag.[Name] in ({{filterValues}})"}]

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - ACD Presented
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - ACD Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - NACD Incoming
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:NACD}}' AND dim7.ValueEncrypted = '{{7:Inbound}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - NACD Outgoing
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:NACD}}' AND dim7.ValueEncrypted = '{{7:Outbound}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Agent Transferred
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN Dimension11 IS NULL OR dim11.ValueEncrypted = '{{11:}}' OR dim11.ValueEncrypted = '{{11:n/a}}' OR dim11.ValueEncrypted = '{{11:None}}' THEN 0 ELSE Fact0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Available Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted = '{{9:Available}}' THEN Fact4 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Make Busy Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted = '{{9:Make Busy}}' THEN Fact4 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - DND Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted = '{{9:DND}}' THEN Fact4 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Talk Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact1) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN Fact1 IS NOT NULL THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Hold Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact2) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN Fact2 IS NOT NULL THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Wrap Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact3) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN Fact3 IS NOT NULL THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Available Time
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * SUM(CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted = '{{9:Available}}' THEN Fact4 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{9:Available}}', '{{9:Make Busy}}', '{{9:DND}}') THEN Fact4 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Make Busy Time
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * SUM(CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted = '{{9:Make Busy}}' THEN Fact4 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{9:Available}}', '{{9:Make Busy}}', '{{9:DND}}') THEN Fact4 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - DND Time
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * SUM(CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted = '{{9:DND}}' THEN Fact4 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{9:Available}}', '{{9:Make Busy}}', '{{9:DND}}') THEN Fact4 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - ACD Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Agent Transferred
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * SUM(CASE WHEN Dimension11 IS NULL OR dim11.ValueEncrypted = '{{11:}}' OR dim11.ValueEncrypted = '{{11:n/a}}' OR dim11.ValueEncrypted = '{{11:None}}' THEN 0 ELSE Fact0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Handle Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact8) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN Fact8 IS NOT NULL THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - ACD Presented Not Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Declined}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD Talk Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD After Call Work Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact3 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD Handle Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact8 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD Hold Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact2 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD Talk Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: ISNULL(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD After Call Work Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: ISNULL(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact3 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD Hold Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: ISNULL(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact2 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD Handle Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: ISNULL(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact8 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' AND dim8.ValueEncrypted = '{{8:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Login Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{9:Offline}}', '{{9:n/a}}') THEN Fact4 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - ACD Talk Time
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{9:Offline}}', '{{9:n/a}}') THEN Fact4 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - NACD Talk Time
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:NACD}}' THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{9:Offline}}', '{{9:n/a}}') THEN Fact4 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - ACD After Call Work Time
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100 * NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim6.ValueEncrypted = '{{6:ACD}}' THEN Fact3 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim9.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{9:Offline}}', '{{9:n/a}}') THEN Fact4 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedDimensions.Name: Date Group - 15 min

DimensionTooltips.Name: Date/Time
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Full date and time of a call. During use in a summary report, this field is grouped to the nearest interval with a format of m/d/yyyy hh:mm. If added as a row or column to a summary report, the activity will be grouped by day and hour.
DimensionTooltips.UseTip: This field is your primary filter field for date range. Use this field as a filter to select a date range for your report even if you won't be including this field on the report. In addition, use this field on your report if you want your data grouped by calendar date and interval.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Agent ID
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The numeric identifier for the agent.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Agent Name
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The name of the agent.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Queue Name
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The queue through which the call or other interaction was received.

DimensionTooltips.Name: DNIS
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The inbound number (or other address, for example email) on which the call or other interaction came in.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Media Type
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The media type of the interaction. Could be Voice, Chat, Email, Message, etc.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Conversation Type
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The type of the call: a combination of Inbound or Outbound, ACD or non-ACD (NACD), and Internal or External (e.g. InboundACDExternal).

DimensionTooltips.Name: Direction
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The direction of the call: Inbound or Outbound

DimensionTooltips.Name: Outcome
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Whether the call was answered ('Answered'), was not answered ('Declined').
DimensionTooltips.UseTip: Outbound calls will show an Outcome of 'n/a'.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Status
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: For time tracking, this is the system-defined type of status the user is in. For example - Available, Make Busy, Offline.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Sub Status
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: For time tracking, this is your internally defined type of secondary status the user is in.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Transfer Destination
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Name or number of the destination the call was transferred to by the agent, if they did so.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Transfer Destination Type
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The type of destination the call was transferred to.  For example - Agent, External Number, etc.

DimensionTooltips.Name: Account Code
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The account code, if any, entered by the agent

DimensionTooltips.Name: Classification Code
DimensionTooltips.Tooltip: The classification code, if any, entered by the agent

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - 15 min
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by 15-minute time interval.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Half Hour
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by 30-minute time interval.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Hour
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This field represents the hours of the day.
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: You can use this field in two ways. If you want to limit your report to certain hours of the day (8am-5pm for example) you can filter on this field. In addition, you can add this field to your report to show calls grouped by hour of the day. If you want calls grouped by date and hour of the day, consider filtering on this field, but including the Call Date/Time field instead of this one in your report.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Weekday
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This is the day of the week (Sunday - Saturday)
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If you include this field and your time range spans multiple weeks, the calls for the day of the week will be added together. i.e. calls for Wednesday in week 1 and calls for Wednesday in week 2 will be added together for a total number of calls on Wednesdays.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Day of Month
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This is the number day of the month (01-31).
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If your time range spans multiple months, the calls for the number days of the month will be added together. i.e. calls for June 15 and July 15 will be added together for a total number of calls under the 15 day of the month

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Full Date
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This field represents the date and day of week and is formated as yyyy-mm-dd weekday.
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If you want to group calls by day, use this field. You cannot filter on this field as it is a calculated field. Filter on the Call Date/Time field to get the date range you want, and include this field to group the report by dates.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Month
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by month of the year

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Year
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by year

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Week
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by week

FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total count of calls matching the filters selected.  Use this if you are breaking call counts out by group, agent, disposition, date, etc.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Talk Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total amount of talk time across all corresponding calls.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Hold Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total amount of hold time (in minutes) across all corresponding calls. Hold time is when an agent puts a call on hold -- it is not queue time, when a caller is waiting for an agent to become available.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Wrap Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total amount of After Call Work time across all corresponding calls.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Status Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total time spent in a particular status.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Talk Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent in talk during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Hold Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent in hold during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Wrap Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent in after call work during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Handle Total
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total amount of time spent on calls during the date range covered by the report. (Talk+Hold+Wrap)

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Handle Max
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The maximum time any call spent being handled during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - First Login
FactTooltips.Tooltip: This will be the earliest login for the agent that day.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Last Logout
FactTooltips.Tooltip: This will be the latest logout for the agent that day.

FactTooltips.Name: Count - Logins
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total number of logins for the agent during the interval covered by the report.

FactTooltips.Name: Time - Idle Duration
FactTooltips.Tooltip: The total idle duration for the agent during the interval

DimensionTooltips.UseTip: This field is your primary filter field for date range. Use this field as a filter to select a date range for your report even if you won't be including this field on the report. In addition, use this field on your report if you want your data grouped by calendar date and interval.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by 30-minute time interval.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Hour
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This field represents the hours of the day.
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: You can use this field in two ways. If you want to limit your report to certain hours of the day (8am-5pm for example) you can filter on this field. In addition, you can add this field to your report to show calls grouped by hour of the day. If you want calls grouped by date and hour of the day, consider filtering on this field, but including the Call Date/Time field instead of this one in your report.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Weekday
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This is the day of the week (Sunday - Saturday)
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If you include this field and your time range spans multiple weeks, the calls for the day of the week will be added together. i.e. calls for Wednesday in week 1 and calls for Wednesday in week 2 will be added together for a total number of calls on Wednesdays.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Day of Month
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This is the number day of the month (01-31).
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If your time range spans multiple months, the calls for the number days of the month will be added together. i.e. calls for June 15 and July 15 will be added together for a total number of calls under the 15 day of the month

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Full Date
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This field represents the date and day of week and is formated as yyyy-mm-dd weekday.
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If you want to group calls by day, use this field. You cannot filter on this field as it is a calculated field. Filter on the Call Date/Time field to get the date range you want, and include this field to group the report by dates.

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim6.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{6:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Missed

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - To VM
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim6.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{6:Voicemail}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100.0 * SUM(CASE dim6.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{6:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Missed
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100.0 * SUM(CASE dim6.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{6:Missed}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Abandoned

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - On Queue
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim24.ValueEncrypted = '{{24:Available}}' AND dim25.ValueEncrypted = '{{25:TakeAllCalls}}' THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Logged In
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE WHEN dim24.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{24:Offline}}') THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - On Queue
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN dim24.ValueEncrypted = '{{24:Available}}' AND dim25.ValueEncrypted = '{{25:TakeAllCalls}}' THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim24.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{24:Offline}}') THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Time Idle on Queue
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100.0 * SUM(FACT3) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim24.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{24:Offline}}') THEN Fact1 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100.0 * SUM(CASE dim7.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{7:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Missed
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100.0 * SUM(CASE dim7.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{7:Missed}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - To Voicemail
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100.0 * SUM(CASE dim7.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{7:Voicemail}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Call Duration Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(Fact2) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - ACD Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100.0 * ISNULL(SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{13:Queue}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - ACD Calls Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END)

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - ACD Calls Offered
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{13:Queue}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END)

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - NACD Calls
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD Call Duration Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: ISNULL(SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') THEN Fact2 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - ACD Call Duration Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') THEN Fact2 ELSE 0 END)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - NACD Calls Duration Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: ISNULL(SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') THEN Fact2 ELSE 0 END), 0) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - NACD Calls Duration Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') THEN Fact2 ELSE 0 END)

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Missed
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim7.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{7:Missed}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - Answered
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim7.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{7:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - To Voicemail
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim7.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{7:Voicemail}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - NACD Incoming Calls
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') AND dim16.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{16:Inbound}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END)

CalculatedFields.Name: Count - NACD Outgoing Calls
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN dim13.ValueEncrypted NOT IN ('{{13:Queue}}') AND dim7.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{7:Answered}}') AND dim16.ValueEncrypted IN ('{{16:Outbound}}') THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END)

CalculatedFields.Name: %Pct - Transferred
CalculatedFields.Expression: 100.0 * SUM(CASE dim8.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{8:Transferred}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(Fact0), 0)

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Handle Total
CalculatedFields.Expression: CASE dim7.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{7:Answered}}' THEN Fact2 ELSE 0 END

CalculatedFields.Name: Time - Handle Avg
CalculatedFields.Expression: SUM(CASE dim7.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{7:Answered}}' THEN Fact2 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE dim7.ValueEncrypted WHEN '{{7:Answered}}' THEN Fact0 ELSE 0 END), 0)

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Half Hour
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: Groups data by 30-minute time interval.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Hour
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This field represents the hours of the day.
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: You can use this field in two ways. If you want to limit your report to certain hours of the day (8am-5pm for example) you can filter on this field. In addition, you can add this field to your report to show calls grouped by hour of the day. If you want calls grouped by date and hour of the day, consider filtering on this field, but including the Call Date/Time field instead of this one in your report.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Weekday
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This is the day of the week (Sunday - Saturday)
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If you include this field and your time range spans multiple weeks, the calls for the day of the week will be added together. i.e. calls for Wednesday in week 1 and calls for Wednesday in week 2 will be added together for a total number of calls on Wednesdays.

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Day of Month
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This is the number day of the month (01-31).
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If your time range spans multiple months, the calls for the number days of the month will be added together. i.e. calls for June 15 and July 15 will be added together for a total number of calls under the 15 day of the month

CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Name: Date Group - Full Date
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.Tooltip: This field represents the date and day of week and is formated as yyyy-mm-dd weekday.
CalculatedDimensionTooltips.UseTip: If you want to group calls by day, use this field. You cannot filter on this field as it is a calculated field. Filter on the Call Date/Time field to get the date range you want, and include this field to group the report by dates.

CalculatedFields.Name: Average Handle Time
CalculatedFields.Expression: var totalHandleCount = data.totalAcdCalls + data.totalNacdCalls;  return totalHandleCount && (data.totalHandleTime / totalHandleCount)

CalculatedFields.Name: Total Calls
CalculatedFields.Expression: return data.totalAcdCalls + data.totalNacdCalls

Dimensions.Name: Queue Name
Dimensions.SourceColumn: from queuelist select queueName; subscribe queueStatus

CalculatedFields.Name: % Abandoned Today
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAbandonedToday / data.numOfferedToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: % Answered Today
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * (data.numAnsweredToday / data.numOfferedToday)

CalculatedFields.Name: % Service Level Today
CalculatedFields.Expression: return 100 * ((data.numAnsweredToday - data.numOverSLAToday) / (data.numAnsweredToday + data.numAbandonedToday - (data.includeAbandonedCalls ? data.numAbandonedUnderSLAToday : 0)))
